 </a>
<figcaption>PlayStation 30th anniversary desktop - PS3 version. | <span>Image credit: <cite>Eurogamer / Sony</cite></span></figcaption>
</figure>
<figure>
<a data-lightbox="true" href="https://assetsio.gnwcdn.com/playstation_-_ps_30th_2024-12-02_15-53-06_720.png?width=1920&amp;height=1920&amp;fit=bounds&amp;quality=80&amp;format=jpg&amp;auto=webp" target="_blank">
